definition.value: A member of the lclass of pyrrolidin-2-ones that is pyrrolidin-2-one bearing a 3-(cyclopentyloxy)-4-methoxyphenyl substituent at the 4-position.  It is a type IV-specific phosphodiesterase (PDE4) inhibitor.
A cardiolipin in which all four of the phosphatidyl acyl groups are specified as hexadec-9-enoyl
